data.description:
NO HOA or City Taxes 


Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom plus flex room and 2 bathroom home nestled on a large lot in a highly sought-after neighborhood. Upon entering, you’ll be greeted by a bright and airy living room featuring large windows that flood the space with natural light. 

The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating an ideal setting for entertaining family and friends. Boasting ample living space, a dedicated office, a fantastic outdoor area, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, functionality and style.

 The well-appointed kitchen is equipped with everything a chef will need and also includes custom cabinet with plenty of counter space. One if the highlights of this property is the expansive lot surrounding the home. Whether you are looking to relax on the weekends or entertain in style, the outdoor space offers endless possibilities. 

Don’t miss the opportunity to make this dream home yours.
